metadata.name: Ringo
metadata.description:
This NFT is a collaboration with Per Jonsson ( an award winning 3-D artist from Sweden) and myself.
Ladies and Cryptopunks, let us introduce you to “RINGO” ! 
Step Up and be BOLD! March to the beat of your own drum! Live your life to the rhythm of your True Self! And remember to have fun and always bring a clean pair of underwear.
